Author: huhu_matcha
Content:
Kopi Kalyan in Wijaya makes good manual brew.. Indo beans mostly. I went there for a free coffee cupping - enzyme inoculated coffees from Aceh. 

Fuglen has excellent manual brew. 

Common grounds in Ashta has a good Puntang Musara Natural & Anoxic (they‚Äôre slow service but I forgive them because the coffee is consistently good).

Oma Coffee Brewers in Kemang.

Birubeeru cafe in Jakpus. Owner/cafe manager nya Bang Novian. His knowledge of coffee is great.

Espresso Embassy in Jaksel. Not aesthetic but their knowledge is üíØ. I learnt how to roast coffee from them.

Tenun Coffee has just opened up a new cafe in SCBD. I‚Äôve tried their blend from their old cafe

Kala Askara if you want to try other varieties. The barista educates you about coffee. This is the Jkt outpost for their Bandung-based roastery and cafe (Sumthin by Herd)

Author: huhu_matcha
Content: Ngulik kopi pagi ini.. Kamojang by Wanoja Co-op, Jawa Barat. Roasted by Fugol (Bandung). Very prominent taste of lemon tea - quite refreshing
